	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_063532316-battling-cao_hu4fbe707e7b3ca4deff3a92542e396359_337068_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_063532316-battling-cao_hu4fbe707e7b3ca4deff3a92542e396359_337068_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;雄赳赳吓碎老曹肝胆&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;旁边一座忠烈殿，远远能看到里面的黄袍身影，我走进去之前就预料到这里应是供奉着桓侯生死不改的好兄弟了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;进门之后又惊喜——居然亮亮也在这里喔！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_062733165-zhongliedian-gate.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1159&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_062733165-zhongliedian-gate_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_261728_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_062733165-zhongliedian-gate_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_261728_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;忠烈殿大门&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_063004609-zhongliedian-inside.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1159&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_063004609-zhongliedian-inside_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_187581_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_063004609-zhongliedian-inside_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_187581_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;忠烈殿内&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后来到「桃园三结义故里」，布置成了一个农家小院的样子，想来这里应该能是张飞家产的原址，只不过地面上的一切当然都是后人附会的。中间一座结义亭坐着三兄弟的塑像，除了亭旁边布置了几束四时不衰的假花供游客常年拍照外，院内还栽着稀稀落落的真·桃花，让我不由得庆幸，虽然来得晚了点，但还赶上了春天的尾巴，得以看到涿县土生土长的桃花。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_064154699-peachflower.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1159&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_064154699-peachflower_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_418334_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_064154699-peachflower_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_418334_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;结义亭前桃花&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;院里还有一处小亭，亭中「张飞古井」当作是曾经张飞储肉处。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;再往里走，还有另一个内院，当中布置着臆想的张屠户的工作间和演武场，甚至支着兵器架。见到景区工作人员比较宽容，零星的几个游客都上去自己拿起兵器耍起来玩。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_064645070-zhang-fei-well.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1159&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_064645070-zhang-fei-well_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_519719_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_064645070-zhang-fei-well_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_519719_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;张飞古井&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_065545694-spears.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;869&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_065545694-spears_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_250163_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_065545694-spears_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_250163_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;演武场&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;100&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;240px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;兴致所至，我打开小音箱，放在院落一角的磨盘上，循环播放了几遍《这一拜》。可能还被人当成了官方的背景音乐，我看到有另一名游客在周围转来转去，探头看究竟是哪里传出的声音。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;video-wrapper&#34;&gt;
    &lt;iframe loading=&#34;lazy&#34; 
            src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/_JBIQVurk1s&#34; 
            allowfullscreen 
            title=&#34;YouTube Video&#34;
    &gt;
    &lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;游览完毕后，查到三义宫离着不远，因为没什么方便的交通，就步行出发。走出景区之后便是郁郁葱葱的农田，四周天地里一望过去，各个方向却都有不少土堆……像是新坟。让我忽然想起「步出齐城门，遥望荡阴里。里中有三坟，累累正相似。」&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_072806001-field.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1159&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_072806001-field_hu9fd444d66feeba39286d7c1288d8cfc6_276692_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_072806001-field_hu9fd444d66feeba39286d7c1288d8cfc6_276692_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;农田&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;三义宫&#34;&gt;三义宫
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_080150262-construction.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1339&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_080150262-construction_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_219169_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_080150262-construction_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_219169_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;三义宫·建设中&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;154&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;369px&#34;
	
&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_075604431-wall.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1211&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_075604431-wall_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_162240_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_075604431-wall_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_162240_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;三义宫围墙&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;139&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;334px&#34;
	
&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/IMG_20230415_160229-liu-bei-heir.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1752&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/IMG_20230415_160229-liu-bei-heir_huef66d9cc680755227dbe1aa2a8f459b6_351636_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/IMG_20230415_160229-liu-bei-heir_huef66d9cc680755227dbe1aa2a8f459b6_351636_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;《刘备托孤》&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;201&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;483px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;到了三义宫，却发现正围起来装修，只能遗憾地在周围转了转。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;旁边一条「三义宫路」通向附近的村落，路两侧涂着三国故事主题的壁画。沿着路走出去不远就是楼桑庙村，说是纪念昭烈帝的家庙处行程的村落。可惜这里不是真正的昭烈故里「大树楼桑村」，彼处还隔着很远，而且看起来交通很不便利，就只好放弃了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084414156-lousangmiao-village.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1920&#34;
	height=&#34;756&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084414156-lousangmiao-village_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_246064_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084414156-lousangmiao-village_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_246064_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;美丽的家乡——楼桑庙村&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;253&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;609px&#34;
	
&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084634663-lousangmiao.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;652&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084634663-lousangmiao_hud064cda110817952d5d2c89eeb8b08f4_146697_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084634663-lousangmiao_hud064cda110817952d5d2c89eeb8b08f4_146697_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;楼桑庙&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;75&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;180px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;三义广场&#34;&gt;三义广场
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084823850-sanyi-place.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1158&#34;
	height=&#34;869&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084823850-sanyi-place_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_223751_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.nautile.one/post/2023-04-15-zhuozhou-pagoda-peachflower/PXL_20230415_084823850-sanyi-place_hubd58b5eea90ff3475e2027d31ae65ea9_223751_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;三义广场&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;319px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;沿着路一直走，路的尽头是三义广场。到了广场才总算有了些热闹的气息。广场中间立着刘关张骑马像，周围聚着很多居民闲坐或是跳舞。从安静的村落一路走来，走到这里才算是看到了人烟。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;广场毗邻着国道，虽然依旧没什么公共交通，但好在很容易地叫到网约车，回到市区里，乘到公交踏上了归途。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;走了这一趟，感觉仿佛与昭烈和桓侯有了一种神奇的连接。虽然也不是没去过成都，但这样来到他们出生的地方，像是又更深一步地探索到了他们人生的另一个片段。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然而还是遗憾，没能看到开着的三义宫，也因为交通所限没能去到大树楼桑村和卢植墓址，但愿以后还能有机会再自驾来一趟弥补缺憾。&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
